race.comment: There will be loads of pressure up front which will aid BLANTONS RUN (2) who resumes from a spell. Would prefer a little longer but does go very well fresh and has the ability. Aided by the claim and will be charging home late. MISS LEANA (9) scored a big win last time at Gatton over the 860m dash. This is a stiffer assignment but is honest and will give a sight. VEGA NOVA (6) resumes form a long spell with an all the way win here fresh. Will strip fitter and take running down again. ELRONTE (7) resumes on the back of two trials. Speedy filly well placed with the claim and low draw and will give a sight fresh.
